Notes: SP No. 9 and EC No. 19 in this week's WBCA DIII poll.
Boehning scored 8 and Schultz 6 during a 20-1 run that turned a 21-18 deficit
into a 38-22 halftime lead during the final 8:32 of the first half.  EC never
got closer than nine in the 2nd half.  SP sweeps the season series.
Game.Location: W. L. Zorn Arena - Eau Claire, Wis.
Game.Officials: Scott Doberstein,  Lou Pitt,  Joe Stieber
